title: the simplehuman app
description:
The simplehuman app is like having your own simplehuman personal assistant. Use it to keep track of the custom liner code for your simplehuman trash cans. Activate auto-deliveries for liners and soap so you never run out. Adjust, pause or cancel deliveries at any time - with no commitments. You can also register products instantly and keep track of the warranty. The information is always there at your fingertips.

Learn more:
http://www.simplehuman.com/iosapp

To download on the App Store:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/simplehuman/id943280497?mt=8
